<h4>Game Guide:</h4>
<h5>~ When one Character attacks another:</h5>
<h6>* The victim will lose health points = 10 * element_multiplier * chance damge!</h6>
<p style="text-indent: 5em;">element_multiplier = 2 if attacker's element is the victim's element's weakness</p>
<p style="text-indent: 5em;">chance damage = some percent 0.7 to 1.3 </p>
<h6>* The attacking Character will gain 10 experience points!</h6>
<h6>* If the attacking Character reaches 100 EXP, it will level up!</h6>

